  "description": {
    "zh": "实际上，我需要另一个忙。\n\n我的一些人也参与了走私生意，问题是他们有点装备不足，因为他们不是在我的指挥下做这项工作，更像是“他们自己的事”，我想你们年轻人会称之为“副业”？嗯……总之，我们把这解决掉吧，好吗？\n\n如果你只能用双手握着步枪，你就不能携带任何东西，嗯？我决定介入，并帮助我的兄弟们一点，至少以某种方式帮助，如果我让我的家伙们那样受苦，那我算什么老板，嗯？嗯我不是那种人，我想你也不会是，所以如果你有兴趣……你知道——在这里帮助一个朋友？\n\n我当然愿意补偿你的麻烦，所以如果你这个月想要一份额外的薪水，帮我们收集几个大背包。",
    "en": "Actually, I need another favor.\n\nFew of my guys have been engaged in the smuggling business aswell, the thing is that they are kinda under-geared, since they don't do this work under my command but more as \"their own thing\", I think you young folks would call it a \"side hustle\"? Well... Anyway, let's get this out of the way then, shall we?\n\nYou can't carry anything if you have you use your only two hands to hold your rifle, eh? I decided to step in, and help my boys out a bit, help in some way at least, what kind of boss would I be if I'd let my guys suffer like that, huh? Well I ain't that kind of person, and I don't think you'd be either, so if you're interested in... you know - Helping out a friend here?\n\nI'm willing to compensate you for your trouble of course, so if you want an extra paycheck this month help us gather a few large backpacks."
  },
